Class Beverage

java.lang.Object
Beverage
Direct Known Subclasses:
Alcohol, Coffee, Smoothie
public abstract class Beverage
extends java.lang.Object
This class is an abstract class that holds general data about a beverage that can be ordered from the beverage shop. Classes representing the specific types of beverages available should inherit from this class.
Version:
1, 05/05/2021
Author:
Jessica Bunting
